          "KK"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "In life you had a knack for hiding things.  You dropped out of high school but you learned how to hide money from your father. He'd been a tax lawyer, but he was disbarred when you were still in diapers. That's when he started making his living moving money around for bookies, drug dealers and pimps.  When he had got on the wrong side of the Goth crime he ran for it and left you and your mother behind.  You never forgave him for abandoning you, but you used the skills he'd given you to keep your family alive... and you were better at it then he ever wise. In fact it was the Goth's who gave you your big break, handling the family's 'off the books' books.  Getting shot full of holes by a rival mob wasn't part of the plan though.  Luckily, the boss himself scooped you up off the street and gave you his own blood. Your embrace was a breach of something the Camarilla called the Masquerade so you had to leave New York to run the Goth's operations in Las Vegas. It was tough leaving your family, but being a vampire you figured it was for the best.  In Las Vegas things didn't go so smooth.  The Giovanni and Setites were running everything, the Camarilla was just a cutout for their operations. After a few decades of hustling and losses in Vegas the bosses in NYC were getting suspicious of you, so you knew it was time to strike out on your own. Now you're in LA, an independent operator looking to start your own operation and hide your own money and some you skimmed off the top."
        ],
